{"tid":1020943,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【趕時間？】女郎電單車後座當街剃毛 女網民：我都試過","createTime":"2019-02-14T02:44:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-14T02:47:09.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"04ce7b51a5bba434775bb91fb4a3ce82e1339c3c","tid":1020943,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T02:44:12.000Z","msg":"美國佛羅里達州一名女子乘坐電單車時，當街用剃刀刮掉大腿上的毛，被最少兩名巿民拍下短片，並於上周上載社交媒體，廣為瘋傳。有女網民承認，自己都做過相同行為。<br />\n第一段影片顯示，一名穿著看似是露背泳衣的女子，坐在電單車後座，並趁塞車期間，用剃刀刮掉大腿上的毛，再把刀上的毛髮，甩在地上。第二段影片顯示電單車的男司機，正在風馳電掣，但泳衣女子仍用剃刀刮大腿內側。<br />\n截至周三，兩段影片已經有90萬人次瀏覽，不少網民都嘖嘖稱奇，但有女網民「懺悔」，自己讀中學時都曾在上學途中剃毛。亦有人指，在馬路上剃毛總比在游池剃好。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190214/large/1550087336_acb1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190214%2Flarge%2F1550087336_acb1.jpg&h=01965c3d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190214/59256982\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190214%2F59256982&d=uNZXw00WsTXXX%2FAwV3JyEUpSq8GU1PbbWBdRLYKbGpc%3D&h=ef1c09d9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190214%2F59256982&h=215e3041\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190214/59256982</a>"},{"pid":"bd7e522698a4fcdfb1ba0d5664bd0a96f34058f8","tid":1020943,"uid":100661,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T02:47:09.000Z","msg":"以為剃咩毛<br />\n腳毛就算數啦"}]}